---
import fs from 'node:fs';
import path from 'node:path';

// We link to the repository plans.md instead of inlining its content to keep things simple.
const repoPlansUrl = 'https://github.com/kzkaed/kzkaed.github.io/blob/main/plans.md';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Plans</title>
    <style>
      :root { --fg: #1f2937; --muted: #6b7280; --link: #2563eb; }
      body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji"; margin: 2rem auto; max-width: 60ch; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--fg); padding: 0 1rem; }
      nav a { margin-right: 1rem; }
      a { color: var(--link); text-decoration: none; }
      a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Plans</h1>
      <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/plans">Plans</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/kzkaed/kzkaed.github.io">Repo</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
      <p>For now, view and maintain the plan directly in the repository:</p>
      <p><a href={repoPlansUrl}>{repoPlansUrl}</a></p>
      <p>This page can later render the Markdown using Astro content collections if desired.</p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
